<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:09:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列部长与 Black Cube 就监视亲巴勒斯坦的美国学生团体举行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</link><description>侨民事务部长 Amichai Chikli 于 6 月会见 Black Cube，讨论可能对巴勒斯坦学生正义组织执行间谍任务，该组织在美国校园领导反以色列抗议活动。该部称 Black Cube 向其提出了这个想法，但消息人士称事实恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国猛烈抨击以色列斯莫特里奇关于饿死加沙人的言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</link><description>法国和德国外交部谴责这位右翼部长，几天前他暗示国际压力是以色列不让加沙人饿死的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周围的火圈：伊朗、真主党和胡塞武装的军火库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</link><description>从远程巡航导弹到携带炸弹的无人机，以色列的敌人可能会对其防空系统进行前所未有的考验</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</guid></item><item><title>超过 110 名记者在加沙被杀。以色列同行保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</link><description>太多的以色列记者将某种程度的罪责归咎于他们在加沙的同行——甚至认为他们是应该死的努赫巴部队成员</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩担心伊朗和真主党的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</link><description>边境地区的人们正在储存食物和水，等待以色列对贝鲁特的严厉打击。 “哈尼亚被暗杀后，我们意识到我们不能留在黎巴嫩。我们告诉孩子们，情况不安全，我们必须离开。”一位正在回国的法国妇女说道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>“新犹太人”的象征如何最终被装进盒子里——并陷入法律纠纷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</link><description>以色列博物馆展出的伊扎克·丹齐格 (Yitzhak Danziger) 的《尼姆罗德》(Nimrod) 新照片引发了法律和道德争议，引发了一个问题：一件艺术品真正属于谁？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</guid></item><item><title>美国驻日本大使因未邀请以色列而缺席长崎原子弹追悼会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</link><description>该市市长表示，鉴于国际社会对战争的反应，人们担心仪式上会出现抗议、破坏或袭击。加拿大、法国、德国、意大利和英国也发函表达了对以色列被排除在外的共同担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方突击搜查外交部，怀疑在发放外交护照方面存在不法行为——包括向内塔尼亚胡的儿子发放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</link><description>据两名官员称，正在调查的其中一本护照是给总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡的护照</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 09:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</guid></item><item><title>海法居民担心真主党的罢工将针对该市的危险材料港口区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</link><description>在真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉提到海法是火箭袭击的潜在目标后，尽管以色列军队下令减少石化产品库存，但其居民仍担心会发生危险材料事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 的另一场胜利：韦斯利·贝尔 (Wesley Bell) 和 850 万美元击败“小队”成员科里·布什 (Cori Bush)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</link><description>亲以色列游说团体的联合民主项目称赞这一结果“进一步证明亲以色列是两党的好政策和好政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</guid></item><item><title>西方大国越来越担心俄罗斯与伊朗的合作不断发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</link><description>在有报道称俄罗斯正在向伊朗提供军事援助并试图向胡塞武装提供武器后，西方外交官发出了警报。一位外交官告诉《国土报》，“俄罗斯的介入让我们非常担心，以色列也应该担心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于真主党来说，以色列痛苦的等待是其报复的一部分，但它仍然希望避免战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</link><description>哈桑·纳斯鲁拉周二在贝鲁特发表了激烈的演讲，但没有明确威胁爆发地区战争——他的组织及其伊朗赞助人显然仍在寻求避免这种情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</guid></item><item><title>白宫：比以往任何时候都更接近停火协议，美国将帮助保卫以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</link><description>戈兰地区委员会：以色列北部居民必须留在避难所附近，并尽量减少不必要的旅行 ■ 白宫：我们比以往任何时候都更接近停火协议 ■ 土耳其正式要求加入联合国法院针对以色列的种族灭绝案■ 真主党声称对以色列北部的无人机袭击负责 ■ 以色列国防军辛贝特称，以色列战斗机袭击了黎巴嫩南