975-dcd6-abf7-7f77c7700000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚被杀后，哈马斯任命加沙领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔为酋长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</link><description>辛瓦尔曾担任加沙哈马斯领导人，也是10月7日事件的策划者，现在将担任该组织的最高政治领导人。这一任命被视为哈马斯向以色列、美国、人质协议调解人和巴勒斯坦公众发出的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵在测谎仪测试中撒谎；检方将逮捕期限延长至周日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</link><description>这些士兵涉嫌情节严重的虐待行为、强奸情况下的鸡奸行为、侵犯权力和不当行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</guid></item><item><title>英国廉价航空公司 EasyJet 暂停以色列航班直至 2025 年春季</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</link><description>由于担心与伊朗和真主党发生重大冲突，易捷航空 (EasyJet) 在取消和暂停往返以色列航班的众多航空公司中名列前茅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，被认为失踪的比尔哈·伊农 (Bilha Inon) 于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</link><description>据军方称，在她家附近发现的证据证实她是被谋杀的。伊农的家人于10月7日宣布了她被谋杀的消息，第二天开始哀悼她和她的丈夫雅科维</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</guid></item></channel></rss>